OL,5, The chancellor is considering cutting  
OL,6, inheritance and business taxes at next 
OL,7, week's Autumn Statement, the BBC has   
OL,8, been told.                             
OL,10,FJeremy Hunt could make such moves, as  
OL,11,Ffirst reported by the Financial Times, 
OL,12,Fdepending on the latest predictions    
OL,13,Ffrom the UK's main economic forecaster.
OL,15,FA Treasury source said no final        
OL,16,Fdecisions had been made, with Mr Hunt  
OL,17,Fto consider such policies this weekend.
OL,19,FThey added it is possible such tax cuts
OL,20,Fcould be delayed until the spring.     
